&lt;p&gt;This is a part-time post - 19 hours per week. &lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;An exciting opportunity has arisen for a Band 3 Decontamination Technician/HCSW to become part of our team within the Endoscopy Unit at Lymington New Forest Hospital. This is a 6 month fixed term contract with the possibility of becoming a permanent role.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are currently looking for an enthusiastic and dynamic individual. We are a JAG accredited unit consisting of 2 Endoscopy rooms undertaking diagnostic procedures.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;State of the art decontamination facilities support the unit to work efficiently and consistently meeting standards set by JAG.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;If you are a committed, hardworking and highly motivated individual with the ability to work well within a team environment, have an eagerness to develop new skills and expertise within an Endoscopy Unit, we would love to hear from you.&lt;/p&gt;
